library(knitr)
library(tidyverse)
library(StrategyUnitTheme)

# set default options
opts_chunk$set(echo = FALSE,
               fig.width = 7.252,
               fig.height = 4,
               dpi = 300,
               dev.args = list(type = "cairo"))

# Set's the base ggplot theme and changes default colours (if the argument
# set_su_theme_colours is set to TRUE)
su_theme(set_su_theme_colours = FALSE, palette = "main")
